	* RUNSON: update

1999-10-16 13:56  millert

	* defaults.c: Error out if syslog parameters are given without a
	  value.  For Ultrix or 4.2BSD "syslog" is allowed without a value
	  since there are no facilities in the 4.2BSD syslog.

